# Nabat project — design source of truth

## Figma file

- **URL:** https://www.figma.com/design/0F0MpE/phanikTZjANEDqdtwYj/Nabat?node-id=0-1&p=f
- **fileKey:** `0F0MpE/phanikTZjANEDqdtwYj`
- **Home page frame:** node `1:2` (Desktop, 1280×3521)
- **Nav:** node `10:89`
- **Product grid:** node `9:68`

When implementing or updating UI, use the **Figma MCP plugin** (`get_design_context`, `get_screenshot`, `download_assets`) against these nodes. Adapt output to this codebase — do not paste absolute-positioned generated code verbatim.

## Brand assets

Official SVG exports live in [`src/assets/svg/`](src/assets/svg/). Prefer these over Figma MCP temp URLs.

| File | Use |
|------|-----|
| `logo.svg` | Crystal mark (header) |
| `logotype.svg` | Wordmark נבט (header → home) |
| `*-crystal-part.svg` | Hero / closing decorations |
| `*-crystal-bg.svg` | Product card shapes |
| `*-bg.svg` | Story section bands (wavy) |
| `nabat-image.svg` | Closing section cluster |

Product photography (PNG) remains in `src/assets/figma/` until replaced.

## Site conventions

- **Language:** Hebrew, RTL (`dir="rtl"`, `lang="he"`)
- **Font:** Fedra Serif H+L (`src/assets/fonts/`), fallback via `src/styles/fonts.css`
- **Colors:** tokens in `src/index.css` (`cream`, `saffron`, `natural`, `rose`, etc.)
- **נבט logotype + logo** → `/` (home)
- **Cart:** icon button in header, drawer overlay (not a route)

## Stack

Vite + React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + React Router. Mock cart/checkout only — no real payments.
